text = "Survive 18 minutes as insects swarm in from every side.

• Tap a tile to place the selected tower
• Tap the Shovel, then a tower, to sell it
• Drag your finger to vacuum up coins and essence
• Tap the tree (or the Skills button) for its skill tree
• Kill enemies to level up and pick an upgrade card
• Watch for warning markers — mini-bosses hit hard

The tree's HP is your life. If it falls, the run ends."

